      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really dependable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles!",
