    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 987.1 Cayman S, powered by the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus. This mid-engine specialist offers superb longitudinal stability and minimized polar moment of inertia. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with tactile precision, showing no signs of synchro fatigue. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by MacPherson struts and multi-link rear geometry for neutral handling. Recent service includes a borescope inspection to confirm cylinder wall integrity and a cooling system flush. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain performance remains sharp and the ventilated four-piston monobloc calipers provide consistent, fade-free deceleration. A purist\u2019s example optimized for driver engagement.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
