      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, with only minor, expected stone chips on the front fascia from highway driving. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free environment featuring well-preserved leather seating and a fully functional suite of premium electronics. Mechanically, this car is in top form; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent professional inspection confirming the engine and transmission are running smoothly. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes are responsive. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 36500.0,
